gnome-shell-extension-stage-manager (1.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add support for GNOME Shell 49 and 50 (Ubuntu 26.04 LTS).
  * Fix: maximized window now returns to its original workspace on
    unmaximize (previously documented but not implemented).
  * HiDPI: thumbnails and previews scale with the system scale factor.
  * Theme-aware styling via stylesheet.css; cards adapt to light/dark.
  * Multi-monitor: sidebar repositions when monitors change.
  * New configurable keyboard shortcut for sidebar toggle (no default).
  * Scroll-event fallback for legacy mice without smooth scroll.
  * Update maintainer details.

 -- Digvijaysing <itsdigvijaysing@gmail.com>  Wed, 13 May 2026 21:45:00 +0000

gnome-shell-extension-stage-manager (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Maximize-to-workspace: maximized windows move to new workspaces.
  * Stage Manager sidebar with live window thumbnails.
  * Configurable settings via GNOME Extensions preferences.
  * Supports GNOME 45-48, Wayland and X11.

 -- Stage Manager Contributors <stage-manager@example.com>  Sun, 15 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0000
